talaga?

735
00:59:48,980 --> 00:59:53,190
Kaya akala ko napakamahiyain mong tao pero...

736
00:59:53,190 --> 00:59:56,390
Nawalan ka ba ng payong?

737
00:59:56,390 --> 00:59:59,210
- Excuse me?
- Mayroon itong piniritong itlog.

738
01:00:00,670 --> 01:00:04,970
Akin na yan! Ang pritong itlog. Oo, akin yan.

739
